-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Qu%C3%BD-T%E1%BB%B5-thu-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-th%C4%83ng-S%C6%A1n-Nam-x%E1%BB%A9-T%E1%BA%A3-m%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%91%C4%83ng-tr%C3%ACnh-ng%E1%BA%ABu-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc/poem-5YnPZj1DPRNHxnrISZqDWg">Quý Tỵ thu phụng thăng Sơn Nam xứ Tả mạc đăng trình ngẫu đắc - 癸巳秋奉陞山南處左瘼登程偶得</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/S%C3%B9ng-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-tr%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-tu%C3%BD-h%E1%BA%ADu-mi%E1%BA%BFn-nhi%C3%AAn-h%E1%BB%AFu-t%C3%A1c/poem-Iq8VG8qwgWeEtu2Nhc0dkg">Sùng Nhượng trạch đông đình tuý hậu miến nhiên hữu tác - 崇讓宅東亭醉後沔然有作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Th%C3%A0nh-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/poem-ZXawCkOZLOGpQvDaqpfSSw">Thành thượng - 城上</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%B1u-T%C3%A2n/Ti%C3%AAn-tr%C3%A0-thu%E1%BB%B7-k%C3%BD/poem-8WwuSop69rG9-aoxa8C2nQ">Tiên trà thuỷ ký - 煎茶水記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%B1u-T%C3%A2n/author-MfG9Dcv0CtbGpIaXvmxDnA">Trương Hựu Tân</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
